Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:09.71,0:02:11.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人與人之間串聯起來的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:11.84,0:02:13.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使是微小的聲音也會變大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:14.71,0:02:16.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人與人之間串聯起來的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:16.72,0:02:17.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生命就能夠延長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:18.80,0:02:19.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:26.93,0:02:29.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Layer:06 KIDS
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.93,0:03:05.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玲音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.43,0:03:07.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我進來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.83,0:03:35.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玲音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.90,0:03:57.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.73,0:04:01.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若是那個暫存內存的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.03,0:04:03.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經特地減少了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.91,0:04:09.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個真是奇怪
;這句fosky實在是翻的太…
;Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.62,0:04:16.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 我的升學路向要快點決定比較好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.62,0:04:16.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 下一代的協議要快點決定比較好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.34,0:04:18.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣我也可以…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.51,0:04:25.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 你們為何對我這麼好？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.72,0:04:31.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒有這麼想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.23,0:04:33.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是有點不可思議而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.94,0:04:37.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我一向很少朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.90,0:04:44.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝各位 KNIGHTS的各位
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.03,0:04:47.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.81,0:05:57.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還真用功啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.90,0:06:04.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玲音 你好像又變回原本的你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.40,0:06:08.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我們一起玩吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.41,0:06:13.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己一個人的話 人生會變得太灰暗的喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.00,0:06:16.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我不是一個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.83,0:06:18.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有誰？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.00,0:06:20.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家會找我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.00,0:06:25.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不應該這麼說 應該是說我去找他們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:26.21,0:06:27.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.42,0:06:28.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在說網絡嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.30,0:06:33.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,網絡上啊 是沒有真正的友情的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.72,0:06:35.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麗華 你的想法真落伍啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.60,0:06:37.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真落伍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.52,0:06:40.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,落伍又怎麼樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.23,0:06:44.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 玲音到底你在跟誰來往？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.40,0:06:49.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秘密
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.53,0:06:52.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就說是白費工夫了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.62,0:06:53.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才沒這回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.33,0:06:58.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得這邊的更好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.00,0:07:00.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是 我說不用比較好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.71,0:07:02.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得這件更好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.50,0:07:05.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說這件才是最好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.09,0:07:08.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真給你氣死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.26,0:07:11.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挑了三十分鐘 連一件也挑不到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.01,0:07:11.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.51,0:07:13.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我肚子餓了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.82,0:07:33.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 發生了什麼事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.83,0:07:42.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那小孩在幹什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.96,0:07:44.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道在做什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.21,0:07:47.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.71,0:07:48.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧 玲音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.13,0:08:35.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玲音 怎麼了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.51,0:08:37.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.10,0:08:41.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.60,0:08:43.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,討厭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.81,0:08:48.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玲音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:21.01,0:09:22.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近真早回家啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.02,0:09:32.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反而是玲音卻常晚回家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.70,0:09:40.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,推薦的事沒問題吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:43.33,0:09:43.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回來了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.51,0:10:02.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天東京上空 發生不尋常現象
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.01,0:10:04.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,引起街上群眾恐慌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.10,0:10:09.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這現象是人為惡作劇 還是自然現象？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.23,0:10:12.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有關當局正在查證
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.61,0:10:13.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hello 電腦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.11,0:10:15.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hello 玲音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.53,0:10:18.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連上網絡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.92,0:10:39.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是玲音？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.51,0:10:44.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你實在太厲害了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:44.72,0:10:49.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你竟能脫離真實世界來到這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:50.40,0:10:51.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自社貓 快替我蒐集資料
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.32,0:10:58.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要找什麼 以我的等級 已經很勉強了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:59.53,0:11:01.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只靠聽說的人太多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.20,0:11:04.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是不是比他們好多呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.12,0:11:07.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,廢話少說 快點找
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:08.62,0:11:10.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要其它人知道我幫助玲音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.33,0:11:13.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我便會成為這裡的英雄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:13.50,0:11:14.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真多話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.50,0:11:18.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想知道最近小學生流行什麼遊戲？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.13,0:11:19.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遊戲？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:20.13,0:11:22.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小孩子的遊戲有很多款式
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:22.93,0:11:23.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不中用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.43,0:11:27.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的直覺認為那些是遊戲？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.52,0:11:29.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小孩子什麼都能當遊戲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.23,0:11:35.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來你找了博士幫忙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.02,0:11:40.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此 他可能能幫你解決問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.20,0:11:47.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,專門研究兒童的科學家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.71,0:11:56.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是玲音 原來已經對他做了調查
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.50,0:12:01.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他在現實世界裡只是個在等死的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:06.60,0:12:08.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經幫了你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:10.02,0:12:11.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一點點吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.90,0:12:16.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,問問有關「KIDS」的事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:19.73,0:12:23.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了 沒你的事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.41,0:12:28.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,霍金森教授
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.83,0:12:31.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請你告訴我你的過去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.04,0:13:14.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小妹妹 你看起來真活潑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:16.50,0:13:17.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「KIDS」是什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.42,0:13:22.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真令人舒服的時間啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.13,0:13:25.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真希望在我有生之年
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.13,0:13:29.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能一直在這裡度過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:31.93,0:13:33.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道在發生什麼事的？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.81,0:13:36.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「KIDS」到底是什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:37.60,0:13:42.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有了「KIDS」便有美好的時光永恆的寧靜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.82,0:13:43.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,霍金森教授
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:44.32,0:13:46.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請讓我看看十五年前的實驗資料
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.32,0:13:52.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我並不想那些孩子們暴露在危險當中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.12,0:13:55.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那已經不只是十五年前的事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.33,0:13:59.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在那些小孩子正流行玩那遊戲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.13,0:14:02.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那應該是你實驗的重現不是嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:03.80,0:14:07.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來是有人在廢棄箱裡找到了我的資料
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:07.72,0:14:11.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我本想毀滅所有的數據
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.31,0:14:15.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請把那次實驗的事告訴我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.40,0:14:24.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差異 大部分兒童的本身
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.53,0:14:29.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都擁有微少的超能力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.83,0:14:36.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但這超能力並不是一股強大的力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.71,0:14:40.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是直覺之類的 或是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.50,0:14:43.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一種細微的物理現象
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.13,0:14:46.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戴在頭上的是什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.13,0:14:50.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們稱之為能量集中收集器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.72,0:14:53.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通過它來收集能量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.10,0:14:58.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是「KIDS」了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.02,0:15:00.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們把每個小孩的微弱能量結合
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:00.81,0:15:04.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若是能儲存這些能量的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:05.11,0:15:06.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你期待著什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:07.03,0:15:08.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒有想過會有什麼後果
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.20,0:15:11.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是想知道而已 小妹妹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:14.12,0:15:15.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你讓他們做了什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.20,0:15:19.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有理論而沒有證據的話 就不是科學了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.33,0:15:22.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是我一貫的想法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.00,0:15:23.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是在問這些
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.13,0:15:30.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒為那些小孩想過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:30.30,0:15:31.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 如你所說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.30,0:15:37.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受過能量集中器攝取能量的小孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:38.02,0:15:43.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會受到電磁波而干擾腦部  使一部分的腦受到傷害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.11,0:15:46.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是「KIDS」系統的副作用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.41,0:16:00.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當時你到底收集了多少孩子的能量？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.34,0:16:06.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真殘忍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.42,0:16:09.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要…夠了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:12.13,0:16:16.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實我已經把「KIDS」系統完全粉碎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:20.73,0:16:26.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但不知為何設計圖會在網上流傳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.40,0:16:30.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼久了 我以為它已消失了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:31.03,0:16:33.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是被某人找到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.91,0:16:38.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且居然不需要能量集中器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:38.62,0:16:40.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就能做出異象
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:41.20,0:16:42.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他能夠加以改良
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.92,0:16:45.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又有能耐做到這種地步
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.21,0:16:48.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實在是很不簡單
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:49.00,0:16:51.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該值得稱讚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:51.63,0:16:53.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你只會這樣想嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:53.51,0:16:56.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一點都不在意那些小孩嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:57.10,0:16:59.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就算怎麼想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.51,0:17:04.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小孩也不能回到現實世界了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:04.94,0:17:08.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使我關心他們 也是無法彌補過錯的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:10.61,0:17:11.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是不負責啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:13.36,0:17:14.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那現在那個正在運轉中嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:15.32,0:17:16.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小妹妹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:19.16,0:17:21.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經把所有的都告訴你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:22.41,0:17:24.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很高興能見到你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:24.91,0:17:28.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道你在網上是想做什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.42,0:17:31.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不知道你想以後以什麼身份上網
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.30,0:17:36.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論如何 我覺得你非常能幹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:36.51,0:17:39.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若電腦網絡上真的有神存在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:40.01,0:17:42.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他一定會眷顧你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.93,0:17:45.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不覺得…我有何特別
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:47.73,0:17:51.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟利用「KIDS」系統製造惡作劇的人比較
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:51.73,0:17:54.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰的力量比較強呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:56.11,0:17:57.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惡作劇？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:59.70,0:18:02.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 請讓我先告退
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:02.83,0:18:04.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要跟小妹妹你說再見了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:05.62,0:18:09.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的肉體也差不多了 很高興能跟你談話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:10.50,0:18:14.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的心願…完成了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:39.82,0:18:40.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,KNIGHTS
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.34,0:18:52.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好煩呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.63,0:19:01.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們到底是誰？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:02.93,0:19:05.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要教我這麼多東西？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:10.02,0:19:12.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們把我當作玩具嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:12.81,0:19:14.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部是遊戲而已嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:14.73,0:19:16.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,利用那些小孩到底有何企圖？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:17.74,0:19:19.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是為了有趣而已嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:22.62,0:19:26.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了開心就可任意妄為嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:30.33,0:19:32.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這跟畜牲有何分別？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:39.63,0:19:40.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為何不出聲？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:41.22,0:19:42.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒人回答嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:29.72,0:20:30.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是他們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:31.73,0:20:32.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來是這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:49.08,0:20:50.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:52.54,0:20:53.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們倆就是KNIGHTS
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:59.30,0:21:00.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒有猜錯吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:00.71,0:21:01.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們就是KNIGHTS吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:05.93,0:21:06.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快趴下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:12.43,0:21:12.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:14.81,0:21:17.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的房間冷卻系統
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:21.74,0:21:25.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在電腦的冷卻系統裝上了平均器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:26.32,0:21:27.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一副不關你們的事的樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:30.41,0:21:32.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是我們幹的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:34.71,0:21:35.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是誰？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:39.71,0:21:40.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是誰幹的？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:46.63,0:21:47.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是KNIGHTS
